<bibRefCitation author="Causey, N. B." box="[964,1128,1228,1255]" pageId="7" pageNumber="282" pagination="179 - 184" refId="ref10808" refString="Causey, N. B. (1958) New records and descriptions of a new genus and a new species of millipeds of the family Striariidae (Chordeumida). Proceedings of the Biological Society of Washington, 71, 179 - 184." type="journal article" year="1958">Causey (1958)</bibRefCitation>
